== How to enter flash mode ==
hold Power On and Volume Down buttons while device is powered off.

== Installation ==
$ pmbootstrap checksum linux-motorola-perry<br>
$ pmbootstrap kconfig check<br>
$ pmbootstrap build linux-motorola-perry<br>
$ pmbootstrap checksum firmware-motorola-perry<br>
$ pmbootstrap build firmware-motorola-perry<br>
$ pmbootstrap checksum device-motorola-perry<br>
$ pmbootstrap build device-motorola-perry<br>
$ pmbootstrap install<br>
plug the device and switch to fastboot<br>
$ pmbootstrap flasher flash_kernel<br>
$ pmbootstrap flasher flash_rootfs<br>

